  m_Name: NeighborJournal_22
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::JournalData
  id: 44
  title: "Nh\u1EADt k\xFD h\xE0ng x\xF3m #22 \u2014 Nh\xE2n ch\u1EE9ng"
  category: 3
  content: "T\xF4i l\xE0m vi\u1EC7c trong ph\xF2ng lab t\u1EA7ng 3 b\u1EC7nh vi\u1EC7n.
    H\xF4m tr\u01B0\u1EDBc t\xF4i th\u1EA5y m\u1ED9t thanh ni\xEAn kh\u1ECFe m\u1EA1nh
    t\xEAn Ethan \u0111\u1EBFn g\u1EB7p BS. Edward. H\u1ECD n\xF3i chuy\u1EC7n r\u1EA5t
    l\xE2u, r\u1ED3i Ethan k\xFD m\u1ED9t t\u1EDD gi\u1EA5y. BS. Edward \u0111\u01B0a
    cho anh ta m\u1ED9t phong b\xEC d\xE0y. Sau \u0111\xF3 Ethan v\xE0o ph\xF2ng
    th\u1EED nghi\u1EC7m. T\xF4i kh\xF4ng bi\u1EBFt h\u1ECD l\xE0m g\xEC b\xEAn trong,
    nh\u01B0ng h\xF4m sau t\xF4i kh\xF4ng th\u1EA5y Ethan ra kh\u1ECFi ph\xF2ng n\u1EEFa.
    BS. Edward n\xF3i Ethan \u0111\xE3 xu\u1EA5t vi\u1EC7n. Nh\u01B0ng t\xF4i th\u1EA5y
    \xE1nh m\u1EAFt \xF4ng ta n\xE9 tr\xE1nh khi n\xF3i. C\xF3 g\xEC \u0111\xF3 kh\xF4ng
    \u1ED5n. T\xF4i ghi l\u1EA1i \u0111\xE2y ph\xF2ng khi c\u1EA7n."
  image: {fileID: 0}
  voiceLog: {fileID: 0}
